T*
(Quick CSS Concepts You Just Used) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(- [IMPORTANT] max-width + margin: 0 auto = centered content block on large screens.) Tj
T*
(- [IMPORTANT] display: flex + flex-wrap: wrap = responsive row that can stack naturally.) Tj
T*
(- [IMPORTANT] flex: 1 1 320px = grow and shrink, with a preferred base width.) Tj
T*
(- [IMPORTANT] Media queries \(@media\) = apply rules only for certain viewport widths.) Tj
T*
(- [IMPORTANT] height: auto = let content control the box height.) Tj
T*
(- @keyframes + animation = create entry transitions.) Tj
T*
(- prefers-reduced-motion = accessibility-friendly motion handling.) Tj
T*
(- JS measurement + max-height = exact visible card count with variable content.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(---) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(How to tweak this later \(safe edits\)) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(If you want to customize the look further:) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
(1. Wider/narrower desktop content:) Tj
T*
(   - edit main { max-width: 1200px; } in Scripts/CSS/main.css.) Tj
T*
(2. More/less spacing between cards:) Tj
T*
(   - edit gap in .main-first, .main-second, .main-third.) Tj
T*
(3. Faster/slower fade-in:) Tj
T*
(   - edit animation: pageFadeIn 0.7s ... in Scripts/CSS/header.css.) Tj
T*
(4. Earlier/later phone layout switch:) Tj
T*
(   - adjust values in media queries \(900px, 768px, 480px\).) Tj
T*
(5. Tighter/looser stacked header spacing:) Tj
T*
(   - adjust .header-title { gap: ... } and the tablet/mobile flex rules in Scripts/CSS/header.css.) Tj
T*
(6. More/less project cards visible before scrolling:) Tj
T*
(   - edit MAX_VISIBLE_PROJECTS in Scripts/JS/projects-scroll.js.) Tj
T*
( ) Tj
T*
